snippet.title: Man arrested over Melbourne man's death
snippet.content: A man has been arrested over a suspicious death in Melbourne. A 24-year-old man died after being found critically injured near Tottenham station in West Footscray train station on Saturday night. Detectives are waiting on the results of a post-mortem examination but confirmed on Monday they have arrested a 35-year-old man. (C) AAP 2017
